{"tid":613881,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 玩命! 無火即食宮保雞丁飯","createTime":"2018-04-02T05:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T17:27:57.000Z","uid":9298,"like":44,"dislike":352,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"16942ceca9f31ca8dabe5b0c6c4b55342450569e","tid":613881,"uid":9298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:11:30.000Z","msg":"話說有次返大陸見到有好q 多即食xx 既野，睇張圖就幾吸引，加上未食過其他即食xx 系列既野，所以狗衝左一盒宮保雞丁黎試下。<br />\n<br />\n宮保雞丁最重要係食雞既鮮配埋辣既層次而成，咁當然唔能夠期望咁既一盒野有咩質素可言。廢話唔好講，睇圖。<br />\n<br />\n為安全計放係地下做實驗<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ohkqgydj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fohkqgydj&h=11234273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎落幾重下，睇落暫時正常<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xz80rt2o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxz80rt2o&h=12a817c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打開全套<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ctamvj9d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fctamvj9d&h=fc26842e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n竟然跟埋水<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xskipwr7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxskipwr7&h=a84ab5d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信係生石灰，發熱原理其實好簡單，這一種無火加熱的功能是利用石灰發熱包當中的氧化鈣 （又稱生石灰，Calcium oxide）遇水就會放熱的化學反應，轉化成氫氧化鈣（又稱熟石灰，Calcium Hydroxide），釋放熱能並產生水蒸氣，從而煮熟食物。無火火鍋盒蓋設有的小氣孔，原來是用來排走盒內的水蒸氣。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zpeutlx3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzpeutlx3&h=a04b115e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主角1<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hrt5j0sz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhrt5j0sz&h=1d63210f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主角2<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z5rbnptu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz5rbnptu&h=aa3221b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟得水就自然會跟埋餐具<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/54juo7hn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F54juo7hn&h=f704e481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲跟埋個膠袋<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uik0pn9f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuik0pn9f&h=617053d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備爆炸啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/280pwqoy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F280pwqoy&h=99415cee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說明書話要撈9 亂晒先<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hjn8pam1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhjn8pam1&h=1c48d320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\non9左唔記得放左膠袋落底先&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8nmosjhx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8nmosjhx&h=7ea01afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等15分鐘&hellip;唔知會唔會爆炸呢"},{"pid":"34ad25c34b9c8fbee451ba90b5cf87352de421c5","tid":613881,"uid":81120,"like":120,"dislike":0,"score":120,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4920de7952394a775cf39a8e57b4c323fa2494f9","tid":613881,"uid":22087,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"咁重口味 啲雞臭既都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf32b5f43b42f5a7a1568cca8660cc8336b54a6","tid":613881,"uid":174013,"like":432,"dislike":4,"score":428,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/aad1fff0714f46e6cf16f09e30f37885/tenor.gif?itemid=5863256\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Faad1fff0714f46e6cf16f09e30f37885%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D5863256&h=4b8e38c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2390db7cd21a8e30007f6d9daecebf65ab835b58","tid":613881,"uid":20222,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"個袋雞放面得唔撚得架<i